NewsFlash users... (set bbstype%=3 in the basic file if not already done)

Put !BBSstat in the    <NewsFlash$BBS>Doors.NewsFlash    directory

Then use the following script extract to use !BBSstats 
(where 'option' is a variable!)

{
if option = "B" then
 std
 report "BBSstats"
 runtask "<NewsFlash$BBS>Doors.NewsFlash.!BBSstats"
 script "<NewsFlash$BBS>Doors.newsflash.!BBSstats.StatScr"
 gosub anykey
endif
}

Note: the door will have to be run once before it will generate a script!

-Alex-